    "description": "<u>Overview</u><br><br>Join Remy Raccoon in this Halloween special, exploring 12 fiendish new levels filled with tricks, treats and things that go bump in the night.  The creatures of Halloween have stolen Remy's gems and hidden them in the spooky graveyard.  Be warned though, only the bravest adventurer will collect all the gems and progress to the next level.<br><br>*** This is a stand-alone game, so you do not need the original game in order to play. ***<br><br><u>Gameplay</u><br><br>Remy Raccoon and the Lost Temple is a top-down dungeon crawler that sees our furry hero exploring the Lost Temple in search of treasure.<br><br>The object of the game is to collect all the gems from the Lost Temple, avoiding a variety of traps, creatures and other obstacles along the way.  Collecting all the gems from one level will unlock the next, where you will face a new set of challenges.<br><br><u>Game modes</u><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play in <strong>Adventure Mode</strong> to unlock new levels.<br></li><li>Face an unpredictable set of challenges in <strong>Random Mode</strong>.<br></li><li>Replay some of your favourite levels as endurance challenges in <strong>Survival Mode</strong>.</li></ul><br><u>Other cool stuff</u><br><br>Complete bonus challenges along the way to unlock skulls.  Complete all the skull challenges to unlock the legendary Skull of Dominion.<br><br>Your adventure awaits...",
